T02TD1703E:58a-1: a'ary'a t'a ra de b'i sto tra sarba aartha s'a dha na n'a ma sto tra r'a dza /
T02TD1703E:58a-3: 'phags ma lha mo sgrol ma'i bstod pa don thams cad grub pa zhes bya ba bstod pa'i rgyal po /
T02TD1703E:58b-0: mgon po thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang @58b phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:58b-1: zla ba skar ma'i tshogs ltar mkha' la mdzes //
T02TD1703E:58b-2: mgon po sems dpas bskor cing 'gro na'ang mdzes //
T02TD1703E:58b-3: zla ba dri med gdung ba sel ba bzhin //
T02TD1703E:58b-4: mi shes kun spangs 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel //
T02TD1703E:58b-5: byang chub phyogs chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-6: bsam gtan ting 'dzin rnam thar mang po can //
T02TD1703E:58b-7: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan gyis brgyan pa la //
T02TD1703E:58b-8: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus rab tu brgyan //
T02TD1703E:58b-9: srung byed gsum dang ma 'dres dran gsum dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-10: mi 'jigs bzhi brnyes yongs su dag bzhi mnga' //
T02TD1703E:58b-11: stobs bcu'i rtsal ldan skye la thugs rje che //
T02TD1703E:58b-12: bag chags kun bcom mi bsnyel rnam kun bcom //
T02TD1703E:58b-13: rigs lngas nyon mongs lnga bcom ye shes lnga //
T02TD1703E:58b-14: sku lnga mngon par byang chub rnam lnga brnyes //
T02TD1703E:58b-15: lam lnga sbyong mdzad sangs rgyas lnga yi sku //
T02TD1703E:58b-16: phung po lnga spangs zag zad mngon shes lnga //
T02TD1703E:58b-17: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi snying po khyod //
T02TD1703E:58b-18: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas rgyu yi mchog / chags sdang bral yang 'gro ba'i don gyi phyir //
T02TD1703E:58b-19: cha lugs rnam pa sna tshogs 'dzin pa khyod //
T02TD1703E:58b-20: sna tshogs phrin las sku mdog ljang gu can //
T02TD1703E:58b-21: dbu la 'od dpag med pas rab tu brgyan //
T02TD1703E:58b-22: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i cha lugs can //
T02TD1703E:58b-23: 'gro ba'i ded dpon sgrol ma khyod kyi sku //
T02TD1703E:58b-24: mdzes pa'i ral ba dbu rgyan cod pan dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-25: dar dbyangs zla tshes sna tshogs rdo rjes mdzes //
T02TD1703E:58b-26: rna rgyan mgul rgyan dpung rgyan gdu bu dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-27: ska rags zhabs gdub pa da'i smad dkris mdzes //
T02TD1703E:58b-28: rin chen nor bus spras pa'i do shal dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-29: dpung rgyan se mo dos ni shin tu brgyan //
T02TD1703E:58b-30: bcos bu'i ras dang kha dog sna tshogs pa'i //
T02TD1703E:58b-31: dar dang lha yi dar zab na bza' mnabs //
T02TD1703E:58b-32: padma'i rigs ni padma las 'khrungs can //
T02TD1703E:58b-33: sna tshogs padma mchog gi gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1703E:58b-34: chags dang zhe sdang gti mug la sogs kyis //
T02TD1703E:58b-35: ma gos padma dmar po bzhin du dag / dbang po gshin rje chu lha gnod sbyin dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-36: 'byung po me lha rlung lha srin po dang //
T02TD1703E:58b-37: sa bdag steng gi lha tshogs ma lus rnams //
T02TD1703E:59a-0: phyogs skyong 'gro don sbrul mdzad khyod kyi @59a * //
T02TD1703E:59a-2: / tshangs pa khyab 'jug dbang phyug lha chen dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-3: drag po zhi ba au ma la sogs las //
T02TD1703E:59a-4: rgyal gyur lha yi lha ste sgrol ma khyod //
T02TD1703E:59a-5: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug chen por grags //
T02TD1703E:59a-6: thod pa mi 'chad thugs rje'i thod pa can //
T02TD1703E:59a-7: ral pa rnams spangs shin tu dga' bas mdzes //
T02TD1703E:59a-8: g-yang gzhi dang bral mtshan dang dpe byad spras //
T02TD1703E:59a-9: thal bas ma bskus byams pas khyab pa'i bdag / dbyu gu gsum spangs bslab pa gsum dang ldan //
T02TD1703E:59a-10: dur khrod gnas der chos kyi dbyings su rol //
T02TD1703E:59a-11: rked phran cang te'u la sogs sgra spangs nas //
T02TD1703E:59a-12: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cus chos kun sgrogs //
T02TD1703E:59a-13: tshangs skud mi bsnams mya ngan 'das pa'i sku //
T02TD1703E:59a-14: mtshan spyod spangs nas dus gsum mnyam par spyod //
T02TD1703E:59a-15: log sred las byung gdung ba'i dka' thub spangs //
T02TD1703E:59a-16: dam pa'i brtul zhugs ma lus rab tu ldan //
T02TD1703E:59a-17: mtshon cha dor nas shes rab mtshon cha bsnams //
T02TD1703E:59a-18: zhe sdang rnam spangs sgrub pa'i rtsa rgyun gcod //
T02TD1703E:59a-19: phyogs 'dzin mi mnga' grub mtha' kun gyi bdag / chags pa mi mnga' kun la mkha' ltar spyod //
T02TD1703E:59a-20: mtha' spangs nam mkha' lta bur khyod kyi thugs //
T02TD1703E:59a-21: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor thams cad khyod kyi sku //
T02TD1703E:59a-22: sgra dang brjod par snang ba thams cad gsung //
T02TD1703E:59a-23: sgrol ma chos kun bsdus pa'i snying po can //
T02TD1703E:59a-24: zhi dang rgyas dang dbang dang mngon spyod dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-25: dgug dang dgar dang sde rengs bskrad pa dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-26: lkugs dang tshig 'phrog gzugs sgyur bsrung la sogs //
T02TD1703E:59a-27: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi phrin las can //
T02TD1703E:59a-28: sku yi dbang phyug gsung gi dbang phyug dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-29: thugs kyi dbang phyug 'dod yon dbang phyug ldan //
T02TD1703E:59a-30: rdzu 'phrul kun 'gro yon tan brgyad dang ldan //
T02TD1703E:59a-31: chos sku mkha' ltar dbyer med rtogs gyur kyang //
T02TD1703E:59a-32: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon lta bur 'gro la ston //
T02TD1703E:59a-33: ji srid dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag po mchog / sgrol ma 'gro ba 'khor ba'i gze ba las grol //
T02TD1703E:59a-34: gang gis dran na ngan song 'jigs pa dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-35: rgyal po rkun po me chus 'jigs pa dang //
T02TD1703E:59a-36: seng ge stag sbrul srin po'i 'jigs las sgrol//
T02TD1703E:59b-0: @59b 'byung ba 'khrugs dang gdon gyis bskyed pa yis //
T02TD1703E:59b-1: srog 'phrog nad kyi bye brag ma lus dang //

T02TD1703E:59b-5: mos pas dran pa rnams la stsol pa yin //
T02TD1703E:59b-6: rgyal srid 'dod pas g-yul ngor rgyal pa dang //
T02TD1703E:59b-7: longs spyod grags pa 'dod pa de dag dang //
T02TD1703E:59b-8: bkur ba'i dri ngas bral 'dod spyod pa yin //
T02TD1703E:59b-9: gang gis bstod pas bde gshegs kun la bstod //
T02TD1703E:59b-10: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi bskyed mdzad ma //
T02TD1703E:59b-11: sangs rgyas sras bcas ma lus khyod kyi sku //
T02TD1703E:59b-12: rje btsun sgrol ma yon tan phung po can //

T02TD1703E:59b-14: drag po zhi ba au ma dkar sha ma sogs //
T02TD1703E:59b-15: skul byed lu gu rgyud dang khro gnyer can //
T02TD1703E:59b-16: m'a ma k'i dang spyan dang gos dkar mo //
T02TD1703E:59b-17: 'gro ba gang gis 'dul ba de don du //
T02TD1703E:59b-18: ji ltar khyad 'phags brjid pa'i cha lugs can //
T02TD1703E:59b-19: thabs tshul rnam pa mtha' yas ston pa'i sku //

T02TD1703E:59b-23: 'gro don sgrub pa sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //

T02TD1703E:59b-25: phyag stong spyan stong sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //

T02TD1703E:59b-27: mtshan dang dpes brgyan sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-28: zla 'dra'i yan lag sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-29: nyi ma lar gsal sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-30: dus gsum 'gyur med sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //

T02TD1703E:59b-32: chu ltar bsil mdzad sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //

T02TD1703E:59b-34: rlung ltar rgyas mdzad sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-35: sman pa'i rgyal po sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-36: sman ltar nad 'joms sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:59b-37: thugs rje'i chu rgyun sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:60a-1: ba'i thabs mkhas sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:60a-2: sgeg kyang chags bral sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:60a-3: thar pa'i lam ston sgrol ma'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1703E:60a-4: stong nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i chos kyi sgra //
T02TD1703E:60a-5: 'gro ba ma lus pa la nges sgrogs pas //
T02TD1703E:60a-6: mu stegs ri dags skrag mdzad seng ge che //
T02TD1703E:60a-7: rje btsun sgrol ma'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:60a-8: mi phyed rdo rje 'dzin pa'i zhags pa dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-9: chos sgrogs dung dang shes rab mda' 'dzin dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-11: snying rje gzhu dang lta ngan sdigs mdzub mdzad //
T02TD1703E:60a-12: thugs kyi rnam par dag pa brda tshul du //
T02TD1703E:60a-13: rdo rje la sogs rtag tu byin brlabs pa'i //
T02TD1703E:60a-14: phyag brgyad mtshan ma brgyad kyis rab brgyan pa'i //
T02TD1703E:60a-15: rje btsun sgrol ma'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:60a-16: rdo rje sgrol ma rin chen sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-17: padma'i sgrol ma las kyi sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-18: bdug pa'i sgrol ma me tog sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-19: mar me'i sgrol ma dri yi sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-20: lcags kyu'i sgrol ma zhags pa'i sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-21: lcags sgrog sgrol ma dril bu'i sgrol ma dang //
T02TD1703E:60a-22: bcu gnyis 'khor lo'i tshogs kyis rab bskor ba'i //
T02TD1703E:60a-23: rje btsun sgrol ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:60a-24: mgon po 'od dpag med la phyag 'tshal lo //

T02TD1703E:60a-40: thugs rje chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:60a-41: bud med sgyu 'phrul khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1703E:60b-0: ku ru @60b ku lle khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //

T02TD1703E:60b-2: aom t'a re tutt'a re tu re sv'a h'a /

T02TD1703E:60b-5: khrus byas dang bas rtse gcig gis //

T02TD1703E:60b-10: dngos grub ma lus byin brlab 'gyur //
T02TD1703E:60b-11: zla ba yar ngo'i tshes brgyad la //

T02TD1703E:60b-13: rje btsun sgrol ma mchod byas nas //
T02TD1703E:60b-14: bstod dang gsang sngags 'di bzlas na //
